        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Watcher in the Dark: Once per battle, in any phase, just after a mortal wound is allocated to an ADEPTUS ASTARTES model in this unit, this unit can summon a Watcher in the Dark. When it does, until the end of the phase, models in this unit have the Feel No Pain 4+ ability against mortal wounds. Designer\u2019s Note: Place a Watcher in the Dark token next to the unit, removing it when this ability has been used."
